<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Features</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">


<ListItem>
<Paragraph>Essential Chart supports the <Bold>Funnel Chart </Bold> type. In this demo, series displayed in Funnel chart type with its data labels.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>



</List>
<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">


<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Palette"</Bold> helps to apply palette for ChartArea.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The Combo Box <Bold>"Point Gap"</Bold> helps to change the gap between the segments.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Explode Index"</Bold> helps to select a segment to be exploded</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"ShowDataLabels"</Bold> sets the visibility of DataLabels. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

</List>

